[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "「九偉人図」によれば、この辺りにありそうだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00630",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ユミア",
		"romanized_name": "Yumia",
		"model_path_hash": "8553801663070209956",
		"text": "相変わらず大陸って感じではないような？\n不思議な島だね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_164_038_00631",
		"still_path_hash": "3603268135404135156",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "暗黒の氷海内にありながら、吹雪がない。\n気温も安定していて、魔物が寄り付かない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00632",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "マナがたくさん埋まっていたりとかは？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00633",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "残念ながらそれもなさそうだよ。\nマナがまったくないわけではないけれど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00634",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "人の手が入っていない分、他の場所よりはマナが\nありそうですけど、無尽蔵って感じじゃないですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00635",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "果ての大陸の伝承は、でたらめだったってこと？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00636",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "パルメ族が案内人まで用意していた場所だから、\nそんなはずはないと思うけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00637",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "絶対に何か見つかるはず。\nこの大陸……ううん、島を探索しよう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00638",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "みんな～！　こっちになんかあるよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00639",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "大きな門と、それを取り囲むように９つの石碑……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00640",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "これ、パルメ族の文明の「閉ざさずの門」だよね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00641",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ハイディ、知ってるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00642",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "私の故郷、ルイネ州で、およそ２００年前に出土した\n用途不明の謎の門……それにそっくりなんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00643",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "っていうか相棒は錬金党の所で見たことあるでしょ。\n……あ、記憶ないのか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00644",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ついに見つけたんだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_038_00645",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "おめでとう。君たちはたどり着いたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_038_00646",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "本当に待ちくたびれたよ。寄り道しすぎなんだって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_038_00647",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "ここが、あなたがたの旅の終着点です",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_038_00648",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "え？　なに、ここが……？　どういうこと？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00649",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "見ていれば分かる。\nさあ、ここからは俺たちの仕事だ。皆、準備しろ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00650",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "門を、開くぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00651",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]